}
	
</style></head><body class="pdf ko-KR" lang="ko-KR"><article id="33f1aa3f-848d-806a-bd1e-d008d2300e99" class="page sans"><header><div class="page-header-icon undefined"><span class="icon">👍🏻</span></div><h1 class="page-title" dir="auto">Improving Language Understanding by Generative Pre-Training</h1><p class="page-description" dir="auto"></p></header><div class="page-body"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ae-bfda-faa95f4aa4bb" class="block-color-gray_background">0. Abstract</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-80cf-a46e-cfaeb1f67630"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">📌</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8003-8586-ef52e668e295" class="">▪️ 문제 정의 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-801b-91d5-d828804b0f21" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">NLP는 다양한 task로 구성됨 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ca-a04f-c5b2252f4a32" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">라벨 데이터 부족 → 지도 학습 모델 성능 향상 어려움 </li></ul></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8091-b629-e5ae8412ed78" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8079-a9e9-ec721de46459" class="">💡 대규모 텍스트로 <mark class="highlight-yellow_background"><strong>언어 모델 사전 학습 (pre-training)</strong></mark><div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8022-828c-d4025a5eb277" class="">→ 각 task에 대해 <mark class="highlight-yellow_background"><strong>fine-tunning 수행 </strong></mark></p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-8047-b767-c1ca9d74c1a3" class="">하나의 사전 학습된 언어 모델을 다양한 NLP task에 효과적으로 적용 가능 </blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8093-8245-c6e3ae0c2944" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8070-bacb-d8fff63e78fc" class="">▪️ 기존 방법과 차이 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-803c-9cf4-cea3105decc6" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">task-specific 구조 최소화 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-800c-a0e9-f37bea1c2c6c" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">동일 모델을 다양한 task에 적용 가능 </li></ul></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8006-9aab-d76fbf6bee48" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-809c-b5fe-c8abac298681" class="">➡️ <strong>GPT는 pre-training된 언어 모델을 fine-tunning하여 다양한 NLP task를 해결하는 범용 모델</strong> </p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b9-af58-e340c3be2fbc" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="33f1aa3f-848d-8071-9799-f8eb029eb723" class="block-color-gray_background">1. Introduction</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ce-bffb-f0afa910d7b6" class="block-color-teal_background">논문이 다루는 분야 </h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-8079-a8a7-fc5450ca752f"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">🔖</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-800f-a91b-f80c8e1efc19" class=""><strong>자연어 처리 (NLP, Natural Language Processing)</strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b0-8016-ccd2bb196d72" class="">자연어 처리(NLP) 분야에서, 대규모 텍스트 데이터를 활용한 언어 표현 학습과              pre-training 기반 transfer learning에 대한 논문 </blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-806a-8aa3-f2aab76c8df6" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8087-ade8-ce1d2d32b7f4" class="">✅ 언어 표현 학습 (Language Representation Learning)<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8019-b967-dd90ddc03571" class="">: 텍스트 데이터를 이용해 단어와 문장의 의미를 벡터로 학습하는 분야 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-800e-9f89-cf55af817f99" class="">✅ Semi-supervised Learning <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ce-bd0b-d9917cf2452c" class="">: 라벨 없는 데이터 + 라벨 있는 데이터 결합한 학습 방식 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8018-a271-db5897f627ec" class="">✅ Transfer Learning <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-808f-a0e3-faa0eda8a85b" class="">: 한 번 학습한 모델을 다양한 task에 재사용 </p></div></div></p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-801d-b94a-d2a762316ed0" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-8034-b494-cbabcd6c1a47" class="block-color-teal_background">해당 task에서 기존 연구 한계점 </h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-8075-b7b5-d838e90cee13"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">🚨</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-801b-a1b9-cde80caf1770" class="">▪️ 문제 정의 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-804c-872e-c73e139b2579" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">NLP 모델의 경우 일반적으로 많은 양의 라벨 데이터 필요 <div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8059-9feb-e9936e22dc78" class="">→ 실제로는 <strong>라벨 데이터 확보가 어렵고 비용도 큼</strong> </p></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80f5-a9d6-cfa4d4061f6e" class="">➡️ 다양한 task에 모델 적용이 어려움 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8022-b539-fcd12b5d8e0e" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80f9-93dd-efb81a4b217d" class="">▪️기존 접근 방식의 한계 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a9-82e7-fbd2a38b9524" class="">1️⃣ Representation 학습 한계 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-809e-8f05-e36463ac4784" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">어떤 방식으로 좋은 언어 표현을 학습할지 명확하지 않음 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-8068-a9db-eca419ec6461" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">language model, translation 등 다양한 방식 존재 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8058-8d3b-f6590c21d619" class="">2️⃣ Task 적용 방식 문제 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-806a-a6b1-dd9c1b9aab62" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">기존 모델들은 task마다 구조를 변경하거나 복잡한 설계 필요 <div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b6-bd64-c574f5e5ae8a" class="">→ 비효율적 </p></div></li></ul></div></div></p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8095-9cf6-e39a726ad6b7" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-8091-93b2-c19f3fa8b046" class="block-color-teal_background">논문의 contributions</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a1-b790-d07ffa188a2e"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">💡</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h4 id="33f1aa3f-848d-8097-9b0c-f74ec0aeabda" class=""><strong>라벨 데이터 부족 문제를 해결하기 위해</strong><mark class="highlight-default_background"><strong> </strong></mark><mark class="highlight-yellow_background"><strong>pre-training + fine-tunning 방식 제안</strong></mark></h4></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8043-9b73-d23f4e971e02" class="">비지도 학습 (Unsupervised learning) 활용하여<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-809f-8bed-c9c9e3f7ab95" class="">1️⃣ <strong>대규모 unlabeled 데이터</strong>로 <strong>일반적인 언어 표현 (pre-training) 학습 </strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ee-a0ab-f17f798db38f" class="">2️⃣ 이후 각 <strong>task에 맞게 fine-tuning </strong>진행</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80be-afe2-f7118fd3f93a" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-807d-ada2-dff871876d94" class="">▪️ <strong>Unsupervised + Supervised 결합 학습 </strong><div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80cf-8f68-ca97cb0767ef" class="">➡️ 대규모 unlabeled 데이터로 언어 표현을 사전 학습<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80f5-bcca-dae387962b09" class="">이후 labeled 데이터를 활용하여 task에 맞게 fine-tuning 수행 </p></div></div></p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-803b-b5db-dbe85a09fc2f" class="">▪️ <strong>Representation 학습 문제 해결 </strong><div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80fa-9bdf-d1acb8a42abd" class="">➡️ language model 기반 pre-training으로 해결 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8051-8255-e460bba32572" class="">▪️ <strong>Task 적용 방식 단순화 </strong><div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-800e-96b9-d237cc943c1e" class="">➡️ 하나의 모델을 다양한 task에 적용 가능 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80aa-a01b-e6a45e132545" class="">▪️<strong> 범용(universal) 표현 학습 </strong><div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80be-bb51-ccbf0f3b269f" class="">➡️ 특정 task에 종속되지 않은 일반적인 언어 표현 학습 목표 </p></div></div></p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80d6-9607-fc8330a0b032" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="33f1aa3f-848d-802d-bf4c-d615bfa27dc2" class="block-color-gray_background">2. Related Work</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-806d-b24e-cab0714874d2"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">📖</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-808d-b358-edb26d02a223" class="">1️⃣ <strong>Semi-supervised learning for NLP</strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ff-88a3-e2fdda258e98" class="">:라벨이 없는 데이터와 라벨이 있는 데이터를 함께 사용하는 방식 </blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80af-b956-d26178d52c91" class=""> ✅ Unlabeled 데이터로 학습된 word embedding 사용 시 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ae-bb6d-ec80b8e3b16d" class="">여러 NLP task에서 성능이 향상됨 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-802b-a9b4-db567931afe1" class="">🚫 단어 수준 (word-level)의 정보만 전달 가능 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8023-b745-fe5a634d0724" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-805c-9dde-f8524ba4a483" class="">2️⃣ <strong>Unsupervised pre-training </strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-805a-849a-d2506929e974" class="">모델을 직접 task에 학습시키는 대신 좋은 초기값(initialzation)을 학습하는 방식</blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c7-8904-d12d0f865d8c" class="">✅ 딥러닝 모델의 일반화 성능 향상 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8080-8fd8-e404512c91dd" class="">➕ 이미지, 음성, 번역 등 다양한 분야에서 사용 가능 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80cc-a045-fe4bc0976c62" class="">🚫 LSTM 기반 모델의 경우 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8095-8b5c-fe5d3d744dd0" class="">문장의 긴 문맥(long-range dependency)을 충분히 반영하지 못함</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8000-b36d-ed0d9744d20c" class="">➡️ Transformer 구조의 경우 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-807e-ba33-ec94c9c96d8a" class="">더 긴 문맥을 효과적으로 학습 가능 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ee-932a-e66cf5d56275" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-806d-a978-d3371b2de12e" class="">3️⃣ <strong>Auxiliary training objectives </strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a5-b635-ef87142d071e" class="">Auxiliary objective (보조 학습 목표)를 추가하는 것</blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8087-8e05-ee2cccf36fab" class="">✅ 초기 연구에서 POS tagging, NER 등 task에 보조적으로 함께 학습 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8037-854a-d9163652c812" class="">🚫 task마다 추가적인 구조나 복잡한 설계 필요 </p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80da-9cf9-d36725018b11" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="33f1aa3f-848d-807a-81a9-cc4739a7ae54" class="block-color-gray_background">3. 제안 방법론 </h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-806d-bbaf-ef592f5a1729" class="block-color-teal_background">Main Idea &amp; Contribution</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-8058-a0b4-d63ddcb402d3"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">💡</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8056-ae16-c9b04bd9b724" class="">⭐ 전체적인 학습 과정 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8015-9a4b-f58dfbc78440" class="">☝🏻 대규모 텍스트 데이터를 이용해 고성능 언어 모델을 학습하는 것</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b7-b4bf-e4bd9db37531" class="">✌🏻 이후 라벨 데이터가 있는 분류 task에 맞게 모델을 fine-tuning</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-804c-ba5e-cbf291403518" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c7-9dcf-ed6bdb07968b" class="">1️⃣<strong> Unsupervised Pre-training </strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-8070-a8ef-c05aaf084ec5" class="">Language Modeling 기반 사전 학습 </blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-808d-b2d6-c6a3b867dbd3" class="">➡️ 대규모 Unlabeled 텍스트를 입력으로 사용<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8087-ab5a-fdc06e392c05" class="">이전 단어들을 기반으로 다음 단어를 예측하도록 학습 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80df-b4d5-e6deeffafd90" class="">
</p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8098-8a82-cc10c4c164a8" class="">▪️ 학습 목표 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-808c-b715-f6f9d248cf2e" class="">라벨이 없는 텍스트 데이터<style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mi>u</mi><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>u</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex"> U={u1,...,un}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">...</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span></span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span>가 주어질 때</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><figure id="33f1aa3f-848d-806b-b7a0-fc32a365eba0" class="equation"><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><div class="equation-container"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>L</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>U</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>∑</mo><mi>i</mi></munder><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>u</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>∣</mo><msub><mi>u</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi></mrow></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>u</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo separator="true">;</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L_1(U) = \sum_i \log P(u_i \mid u_{i-k}, \dots, u_{i-1}; \Theta)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.3277em;vertical-align:-1.2777em;"></span><span class="mop op-limits"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.05em;"><span style="top:-1.8723em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span><span class="mop op-symbol large-op">∑</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.2777em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">lo<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∣</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2083em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="minner">…</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2083em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">Θ</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80ad-a0a4-e731032e26d4" class="">➡️ 문맥 <style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo></msub><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>…</mo><msub><mi>u</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo></msub><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">u_(i-k) … u_(i-1)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0147em;vertical-align:-0.3552em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3448em;"><span style="top:-2.5198em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mopen mtight">(</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3552em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.1052em;vertical-align:-0.3552em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="minner">…</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3448em;"><span style="top:-2.5198em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mopen mtight">(</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3552em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span>를 기반으로 다음 단어 <style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>u</mi><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">ui</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6595em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">u</span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span>의 확률 최대화 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80eb-86d0-e5f7b8b9de0c" class="">✅ 문장에서 앞에 나온 단어들을 기반으로 다음에 올 단어를 예측하도록 학습</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e8-8d40-c4b1c6f8ab25" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8087-807e-c91278350752" class="">▪️ 학습 방식 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-804b-b2c0-c77f6a15a4f8" class="">:파라미터는 SGD로 학습 </p></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b8-803a-fad4b634f626" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80f0-8dfd-e7150062d1e7" class="">▪️ 모델 구조 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a4-826c-e588bae33923" class="">⚙️ multi-layer Transformer decoder 사용</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><figure id="33f1aa3f-848d-8009-b5bc-df43fe639a9f" class="equation"><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><div class="equation-container"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>h</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>U</mi><msub><mi>W</mi><mi>e</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>W</mi><mi>p</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h_0 = U W_e + W_p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">0</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">W</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">e</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">W</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">p</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><figure id="33f1aa3f-848d-8016-abbd-db651230498b" class="equation"><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><div class="equation-container"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>h</mi><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>t</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>f</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>e</mi><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>b</mi></msub><mi>l</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>k</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>h</mi><mi>l</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">hl=transformer_block(hl−1),l=1,…,n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">an</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">or</span><span class="mord mathnormal">m</span><span class="mord mathnormal">e</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">b</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="mord mathnormal">oc</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal"