</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8068-9e34-eb83a638a2c1" class="">▪️ 모델 출력 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><figure id="33f1aa3f-848d-8017-8083-f3150758c5fb" class="equation"><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><div class="equation-container"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>∣</mo><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>x</mi><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>f</mi><mi>t</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>h</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>W</mi><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">P(y∣x1,…,xm)=softmax(hmWy)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∣</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="minner">…</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mord mathnormal">m</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">so</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mord mathnormal">ma</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">hmW</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-805b-a920-d6df7f332534" class=""><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>h</mi><mi>m</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">h_m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">m</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span> : 마지막 토큰의 hidden state</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8070-b9ac-fb0fe4a866d7" class=""><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>W</mi><mi>y</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">W_y </annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">W</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1389em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span> : classification layer</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-801b-b865-e14b1bd8be1f" class="">➡️ 입력 문장에 대한 각 label의 확률을 계산 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8030-8aef-cde7ab0e4ab8" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8020-a279-dc573ce8cdd1" class="">▪️ 학습 목표</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><figure id="33f1aa3f-848d-809a-82ce-f010b61a7fd6" class="equation"><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><div class="equation-container"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>L</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></munder><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>P</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>∣</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mo>…</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mi>m</mi></msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L_2(C) = \sum_{(x,y)} \log P(y \mid x^1, \dots, x^m)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.566em;vertical-align:-1.516em;"></span><span class="mop op-limits"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.05em;"><span style="top:-1.809em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">x</span><span class="mpunct mtight">,</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span><span class="mop op-symbol large-op">∑</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.516em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">lo<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∣</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.1141em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8641em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="minner">…</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7144em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">m</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8086-89b8-d2fc61ef5771" class="">➡️ 정답 label의 확률을 최대화 하도록 학습 (log-likelihood)</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-807d-93f4-da644855a642" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-804a-9abb-f6e2ecfeb28d" class="">▪️ 추가 전략</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-8038-8b99-cebd425659a9" class=""><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c7-be78-f80812a385e2" class=""> language modeling objective를 보조적으로 사용</p></div></blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><figure id="33f1aa3f-848d-8064-ae44-c5f0e16ab250" class="equation"><style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><div class="equation-container"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>L</mi><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>λ</mi><mi>L</mi><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L3(C)=L2(C)+λL1(C)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">λ</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b6-b6ef-e64b5745592c" class="">➡️ task loss + language modeling loss 함께 사용</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-806a-b2ac-ce7a85bb94cc" class="">✅ 일반화 성능 향상 + 학습 안정성 증가 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c4-ba86-c2c37a08d413" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8007-97c3-f4789d453b97" class="">▪️ 특징 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c2-8463-e67558969d21" class="">✅ 구조 변경 거의 없음 + 출력 layer만 추가 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80d6-9589-e18f660561ac" class="">➡️ 하나의 모델을 다양한 task에 적용 가능</p></div></div></p></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80a1-acf8-e2ceae5fc47c" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-802e-8047-cb2ce502ffd7"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">💡</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80f4-8fd2-e0b0f99cd40b" class="">3️⃣ <strong>Task-specific input transformations</strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><blockquote id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e2-a0ad-fb7b6c47ddca" class="">모델 구조 변경 없이 입력 변환만으로 다양한 task 처리 </blockquote></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8094-a565-dba7a00fda30" class="">➡️ 모든 task를 sequence 형태로 반환 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8048-9de1-dfd5450ced59" class="">✅ task-specific architecture 불필요</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-801d-9e49-e38886f17346" class="">✅ 모델 단순화 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8059-8b10-e06f8bb0bf19" class="">✅ transfer learning 효율 증가 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8047-9487-c045ff879182" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-806c-90c4-d6d4ffdbe4cc" class="">▪️ Task별 입력 방식 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-8017-b301-d5a5a4403da3" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">Textual Entailment (자연어 추론) <div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-809d-9c64-f5d4fa7e12c9" class="">구조 : <style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>L</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>M</mi><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mi>h</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p[DELIM]h</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">M</span><span class="mclose">]</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e5-b1e8-cbb398d89ffe" class="">➡️ 두 문장을 연결하여 관계 판단 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80bc-9175-c3842b0d3302" class="">
</p></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-80b2-b54c-c180eab0c67e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">Similarity (문장 유사도) <div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80d7-b29b-ccb03c0b5e00" class="">구조 :<style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo separator="true">,</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex"> (x1,x2),(x2,x1)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8005-8b22-fca7b46ea134" class="">➡️ 두 순서 모두 사용 후 결과 결합 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8089-8aa2-d1e882cb2123" class="">
</p></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="33f1aa3f-848d-8071-af9c-ebfe54c8f8b2" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">Question Answering <div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-805e-a2df-d85bb85dd586" class="">구조 : <style>@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.25/dist/katex-swap.min.css')</style><span data-token-index="0" contenteditable="false" class="notion-text-equation-token" style="user-select:all;-webkit-user-select:all;-moz-user-select:all"><span></span><span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>z</mi><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>L</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>M</mi><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mi>q</mi><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>D</mi><mi>E</mi><mi>L</mi><mi>I</mi><mi>M</mi><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>k</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">z[DELIM]q[DELIM]ak</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">M</span><span class="mclose">]</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">q</span><span class="mopen">[</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span><span class="mord mathnormal">L</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">M</span><span class="mclose">]</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">ak</span></span></span></span></span><span>﻿</span></span></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8029-b6d6-fb7458ee88ae" class="">➡️ 각 답 후보를 독립적으로 평가 </p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e2-905e-feed22a060c3" class="">
</p></div></li></ul></div></div></figure></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-804a-8808-fd9b029b1348" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="33f1aa3f-848d-8017-9fe2-c3d521b0b645" class="block-color-gray_background">4. 실험 및 결과 </h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h3 id="33f1aa3f-848d-80c6-8868-f0e786e76a67" class="block-color-teal_background">Dataset</h3></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="33f1aa3f-848d-80e0-9d65-e7ad31feb410"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">🗂️</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8006-805d-ebcadf4baa1a" class=""><strong>Pre-training과 Fine-tuning에 사용된 데이터 셋 구성 </strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8037-b586-c0cf752f6afc" class="">▪️ Pre-training Datset<div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-804b-8fb5-c6246bf72ae5" class="">➡️ BooksCorpus</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-809d-8c24-cb34f0ce7170" class="">✅ 약 7000권 이상의 책 데이터</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-806f-9e1a-e0848686a975" class="">✅ 다양한 장르 포함</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-802c-a284-fcc04a775c93" class="">✅ 자연스러운 문장 흐름 학습에 적합</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="33f1aa3f-848d-8011-baec-f2e1ca9d951f" class="">
