</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="3411aa3f-848d-80fd-94f9-cdc282e5936f" class="block-color-gray_background">5. 결론</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="ltr"><figure class="block-color-gray_background callout" style="white-space:pre-wrap;display:flex" id="3411aa3f-848d-8072-98d5-fdb0cb14f02a"><div style="font-size:1.5em"><span class="icon">💡</span></div><div style="width:100%"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="3411aa3f-848d-80d9-80cb-f17e662018fb" class=""><strong>Generative pre-training과 discriminative fine-tuning을 결합하여 다양한 자연어 이해 task에 적용 가능한 학습 프레임워크를 제안</strong></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="3411aa3f-848d-80f6-90bb-d3b072d8a8a7" class="">
</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="3411aa3f-848d-8047-8e33-c4357e944762" class="">▪️ 핵심 기여 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="3411aa3f-848d-80df-b3a1-d0228afe463e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">generative pre-training과 fine-tunning 결합</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="3411aa3f-848d-8024-8bb4-e34efaa67acb" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">하나의 모델로 다양한 NLP 처리 가능 </li></ul></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="3411aa3f-848d-8091-af83-c87bdf63230c" class="">▪️ 모델 특징 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="3411aa3f-848d-809c-b522-fb8fd96d6cc8" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">긴 문맥(long-range dependency) 이해 가능</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="3411aa3f-848d-8066-8322-ec643895ef23" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">언어적 패턴과 구조 학습</li></ul></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="3411aa3f-848d-8084-a286-c1d84686943a" class="">▪️ 의의 <div class="indented"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="3411aa3f-848d-8061-bd76-d773ae470b68" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">unsupervised pre-training의 효과 입증 </li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="3411aa3f-848d-80d8-9c60-e410b3ea0944" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc">NLP에서 transfer learning 가능성 확장 </li></ul></div></div></p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="3411aa3f-848d-805f-b855-e21685c99853" class="">
</p></div></div></figure></div></div></article></body></html>